msgid "# Qwen3.5-397B-A17B Deployment Tutorial"
msgstr "# Qwen3.5-397B-A17B 部署教程"

msgid "## 1 Introduction"
msgstr "## 1 简介"

msgid ""
"Qwen3.5-397B-A17B is a large-scale Qwen3.5 MoE model that combines "
"multimodal capability, long-context inference, MTP speculative decoding, and"
" W8A8 quantized deployment for production serving on Ascend hardware."
msgstr ""
"Qwen3.5-397B-A17B 是一个大规模的 Qwen3.5 MoE 模型，它结合了多模态能力、长上下文推理、MTP 推测解码和 W8A8 "
"量化部署，用于在昇腾硬件上进行生产级服务。"

msgid ""
"This document describes the main validation steps for the model, including "
"supported features, prerequisites, installation, single-node online "
"deployment, multi-node deployment, Prefill-Decode (PD) disaggregation, "
"functional verification, accuracy and performance evaluation, performance "
"tuning, and FAQs."
msgstr ""
"本文档描述了该模型的主要验证步骤，包括支持的特性、前提条件、安装、单节点在线部署、多节点部署、Prefill-Decode (PD) "
"分离、功能验证、精度与性能评估、性能调优以及常见问题解答。"

msgid ""
"The `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B` model is first supported in `vllm-"
"ascend:v0.17.0rc1`. Use `v0.17.0rc1` or later for this model. The examples "
"below use the version placeholder configured by the documentation build "
"system."
msgstr ""
"`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B` 模型首次在 `vllm-ascend:v0.17.0rc1` 中得到支持。请使用 `v0.17.0rc1` "
"或更高版本来运行此模型。以下示例使用了文档构建系统配置的版本占位符。"

msgid "## 2 Supported Features"
msgstr "## 2 支持的特性"

msgid ""
"Refer to [supported "
"features](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md) to get the "
"model's supported feature matrix, including BF16, W8A8 quantization, chunked"
" prefill, automatic prefix caching, speculative decoding, asynchronous "
"scheduling, tensor parallelism, expert parallelism, data parallelism, PD "
"disaggregation, and ACLGraph support."
msgstr ""
"请参考[支持的特性](../../user_guide/support_matrix/supported_models.md)获取该模型支持的特性矩阵，包括"
" BF16、W8A8 量化、分块预填充、自动前缀缓存、推测解码、异步调度、张量并行、专家并行、数据并行、PD 分离以及 ACLGraph 支持。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [feature guide](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md) to get "
"feature configuration details."
msgstr "请参考[特性指南](../../user_guide/feature_guide/index.md)获取特性配置详情。"

msgid ""
"The support matrix records the maximum verified capability for this model. "
"The startup examples in this document use practical validation settings for "
"online serving and performance testing. Adjust `--max-model-len`, `--max-"
"num-seqs`, and `--max-num-batched-tokens` based on your service workload and"
" available KV cache."
msgstr ""
"支持矩阵记录了该模型已验证的最大能力。本文档中的启动示例使用了实际验证设置，用于在线服务和性能测试。请根据您的服务负载和可用的 KV 缓存调整 "
"`--max-model-len`、`--max-num-seqs` 和 `--max-num-batched-tokens`。"

msgid "## 3 Prerequisites"
msgstr "## 3 前提条件"

msgid "### 3.1 Model Weight"
msgstr "### 3.1 模型权重"

msgid ""
"- `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B` (BF16 version): requires 2 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) nodes or 4 Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) nodes. [Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B).\n"
"- `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8` (quantized version): requires 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) node or 2 Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) nodes. [Download model weight](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp)."
msgstr ""
"- `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B` (BF16 版本)：需要 2 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) 节点或 4 个 Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) 节点。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Qwen/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B)。\n"
"- `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8` (量化版本)：需要 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) 节点或 2 个 Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) 节点。[下载模型权重](https://www.modelscope.cn/models/Eco-Tech/Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp)。"

msgid ""
"It is recommended to download the model weight to a shared directory across "
"multiple nodes, such as `/root/.cache/`, so that all serving nodes can load "
"the same path."
msgstr "建议将模型权重下载到多节点共享的目录中，例如 `/root/.cache/`，以便所有服务节点都能加载相同的路径。"

msgid "### 3.2 Verify Multi-node Communication (Optional)"
msgstr "### 3.2 验证多节点通信（可选）"

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy the model in a multi-node environment, verify the "
"communication environment according to [verify multi-node communication "
"environment](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-communication)."
msgstr ""
"如果要在多节点环境中部署模型，请按照[验证多节点通信环境](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-"
"communication)验证通信环境。"

msgid "## 4 Installation"
msgstr "## 4 安装"

msgid "### 4.1 Docker Image Installation"
msgstr "### 4.1 Docker 镜像安装"

msgid ""
"Select an image based on your machine type. For example, use "
"`quay.io/ascend/vllm-ascend:{{ vllm_ascend_version }}` for Atlas 800 A2 and "
"`quay.io/ascend/vllm-ascend:{{ vllm_ascend_version }}-a3` for Atlas 800 A3."
msgstr ""
"根据您的机器类型选择镜像。例如，Atlas 800 A2 使用 `quay.io/ascend/vllm-ascend:{{ "
"vllm_ascend_version }}`，Atlas 800 A3 使用 `quay.io/ascend/vllm-ascend:{{ "
"vllm_ascend_version }}-a3`。"

msgid ""
"Refer to [using docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-docker) for the "
"complete installation guide."
msgstr "请参考[使用 Docker](../../installation.md#set-up-using-docker) 获取完整的安装指南。"

msgid ""
"After entering the container, verify that vLLM and vLLM-Ascend can be "
"imported:"
msgstr "进入容器后，验证 vLLM 和 vLLM-Ascend 可以导入："

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy a multi-node service, set up the same environment on "
"each node."
msgstr "如果要部署多节点服务，请在每个节点上设置相同的环境。"

msgid "### 4.2 Source Code Installation"
msgstr "### 4.2 源码安装"

msgid ""
"You can also build and install `vllm-ascend` from source. Refer to [set up "
"using python](../../installation.md#set-up-using-python)."
msgstr ""
"您也可以从源码构建并安装 `vllm-ascend`。请参考[使用 Python 设置](../../installation.md#set-up-"
"using-python)。"

msgid ""
"If you want to deploy a multi-node service, install the same version of vLLM"
" and vLLM-Ascend on each node."
msgstr "如果要部署多节点服务，请在每个节点上安装相同版本的 vLLM 和 vLLM-Ascend。"

msgid "## 5 Online Service Deployment"
msgstr "## 5 在线服务部署"

msgid "### 5.1 Single-Node Online Deployment"
msgstr "### 5.1 单节点在线部署"

msgid ""
"Single-node deployment runs both Prefill and Decode on the same node. It is "
"suitable for functional validation, long-context single-cluster serving, and"
" W8A8 deployment on 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) node. The W8A8 version needs "
"`--quantization ascend`."
msgstr ""
"单节点部署将 Prefill 和 Decode 运行在同一个节点上。适用于功能验证、长上下文单集群服务以及在 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G"
" x 16) 节点上的 W8A8 部署。W8A8 版本需要 `--quantization ascend`。"

msgid ""
"Run the following script to execute online 128K inference on 1 Atlas 800 A3 "
"(64G x 16)."
msgstr "运行以下脚本在 1 个 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) 上执行在线 128K 推理。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If the service fails to start, HBM is insufficient, or "
"requests are not scheduled as expected, refer to [FAQs](../../faqs.md) "
"first, and then check the model-specific FAQ in Section 10."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果服务启动失败、HBM 不足或请求未按预期调度，请先参考[常见问题解答](../../faqs.md)，然后检查第 10 "
"节中特定于该模型的常见问题解答。"

msgid "**Key parameters:**"
msgstr "**关键参数：**"

msgid ""
"- `--data-parallel-size 1` and `--tensor-parallel-size 16` set DP and TP for one 16-NPU A3 node.\n"
"- `--enable-expert-parallel` enables expert parallelism for MoE layers. Do not mix MoE tensor parallelism and expert parallelism in the same MoE layer.\n"
"- `--max-model-len` is the maximum input plus output length for a single request. Increase it only when enough KV cache is available.\n"
"- `--max-num-seqs` is the maximum number of active requests scheduled by each DP group. For performance tests, set `--max-num-seqs * --data-parallel-size` greater than or equal to the test concurrency.\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` is the maximum number of tokens processed in one scheduler step. A larger value can improve prefill efficiency but consumes more activation memory.\n"
"- `--gpu-memory-utilization` controls how much HBM vLLM can use to calculate KV cache capacity. A higher value increases KV cache size but can trigger OOM if runtime memory is higher than the profile run.\n"
"- `--enable-prefix-caching` enables prefix caching. For Qwen3.5, short prefixes may not be cached when the hybrid KV cache manager adjusts the block size to a large value.\n"
"- `--quantization ascend` enables Ascend quantization for the W8A8 model. Remove this option when deploying the BF16 model.\n"
"- `--speculative-config` enables Qwen3.5 MTP speculative decoding. Reduce `num_speculative_tokens` or remove this option if the workload is sensitive to first-token latency or if MTP is unstable in your environment.\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` enables full decode ACLGraph replay to reduce dispatch overhead.\n"
"- `--additional-config` enables Ascend-specific optimizations. `enable_fused_mc2` enables MoE fused operators, `enable_flashcomm1` enables FlashComm1, and `enable_cpu_binding` enables Ascend-native CPU binding."
msgstr ""
"- `--data-parallel-size 1` 和 `--tensor-parallel-size 16` 为单个16-NPU A3节点设置DP和TP。\n"
"- `--enable-expert-parallel` 为MoE层启用专家并行。请勿在同一MoE层中混合使用MoE张量并行和专家并行。\n"
"- `--max-model-len` 是单个请求的最大输入加输出长度。仅在KV缓存充足时增加此值。\n"
"- `--max-num-seqs` 是每个DP组调度的最大活跃请求数。对于性能测试，请设置 `--max-num-seqs * --data-parallel-size` 大于或等于测试并发数。\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` 是单个调度步骤中处理的最大token数。较大的值可提高预填充效率，但会消耗更多激活内存。\n"
"- `--gpu-memory-utilization` 控制vLLM可用于计算KV缓存容量的HBM比例。较高的值会增加KV缓存大小，但如果运行时内存高于profile运行时的内存，可能触发OOM。\n"
"- `--enable-prefix-caching` 启用前缀缓存。对于Qwen3.5，当混合KV缓存管理器将块大小调整为较大值时，短前缀可能不会被缓存。\n"
"- `--quantization ascend` 为W8A8模型启用Ascend量化。部署BF16模型时请移除该选项。\n"
"- `--speculative-config` 启用Qwen3.5 MTP推测解码。如果工作负载对首token延迟敏感，或MTP在您的环境中不稳定，请减少 `num_speculative_tokens` 或移除该选项。\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` 启用全解码ACLGraph重放以减少调度开销。\n"
"- `--additional-config` 启用Ascend特定优化。`enable_fused_mc2` 启用MoE融合算子，`enable_flashcomm1` 启用FlashComm1，`enable_cpu_binding` 启用Ascend原生CPU绑定。"

msgid "### 5.2 Multi-Node Deployment with MP (Recommended)"
msgstr "### 5.2 基于MP的多节点部署（推荐）"

msgid ""
"Multi-node MP deployment uses vLLM data parallelism across nodes and tensor "
"parallelism within each node. It is recommended for the W8A8 model on 2 "
"Atlas 800 A2 (64G x 8) nodes."
msgstr ""
"多节点MP部署在节点间使用vLLM数据并行，在节点内使用张量并行。推荐在2个Atlas 800 A2（64G x 8）节点上部署W8A8模型时使用。"

msgid ""
"Assume you have 2 Atlas 800 A2 nodes and want to deploy "
"`Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp` across them. Replace `nic_name`, `local_ip`, "
"and `node0_ip` with the actual network interface and IP addresses in your "
"environment."
msgstr ""
"假设您有2个Atlas 800 A2节点，并希望跨节点部署 `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp`。请将 "
"`nic_name`、`local_ip` 和 `node0_ip` 替换为您环境中的实际网络接口和IP地址。"

msgid "Run the following script on node 0."
msgstr "在节点0上运行以下脚本。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If node 1 cannot join the service or HCCL initialization "
"times out, refer to [verify multi-node communication "
"environment](../../installation.md#verify-multi-node-communication) and "
"[FAQs](../../faqs.md). Make sure the network interface names, IP addresses, "
"and RPC ports are consistent across nodes."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果节点1无法加入服务或HCCL初始化超时，请参考[验证多节点通信环境](../../installation.md#verify-"
"multi-node-communication)和[常见问题](../../faqs.md)。确保节点间的网络接口名称、IP地址和RPC端口一致。"

msgid "Run the following script on node 1."
msgstr "在节点1上运行以下脚本。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If the headless node exits immediately, check whether "
"node 0 is already running, whether `--data-parallel-address` points to node "
"0, and whether `--data-parallel-start-rank` is unique for each node."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果无头节点立即退出，请检查节点0是否已在运行，`--data-parallel-address` 是否指向节点0，以及 `--data-"
"parallel-start-rank` 是否对每个节点唯一。"

msgid ""
"If the service starts successfully, the following information is displayed "
"on node 0:"
msgstr "如果服务启动成功，节点0上会显示以下信息："

msgid "**Key parameters for MP deployment:**"
msgstr "**MP部署的关键参数：**"

msgid ""
"- `--data-parallel-size` is the global DP size across all nodes. In the example, 2 DP ranks are used.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-size-local` is the number of DP ranks on the current node. In the example, each A2 node has 1 local DP rank.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-start-rank` is the first DP rank on the current node. Node 0 starts from 0 by default, and node 1 starts from 1.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-address` must point to the master DP node. Use node 0 `local_ip` on node 0 and `node0_ip` on other nodes.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-rpc-port` is the DP RPC port. Use the same value on all nodes and ensure the port is available.\n"
"- `--api-server-count` controls how many API server processes are started on the master node.\n"
"- `--headless` starts a worker node without exposing an API server. Use it on non-master nodes.\n"
"- `--tensor-parallel-size 8` maps one TP group to the 8 NPUs on each A2 node.\n"
"- `HCCL_IF_IP`, `GLOO_SOCKET_IFNAME`, `TP_SOCKET_IFNAME`, and `HCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME` bind HCCL, Gloo, and TP communication to the selected network.\n"
"- `multistream_overlap_shared_expert` overlaps shared expert computation for better throughput on MoE workloads."
msgstr ""
"- `--data-parallel-size` 是所有节点上的全局DP大小。示例中使用了2个DP rank。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-size-local` 是当前节点上的DP rank数量。示例中每个A2节点有1个本地DP rank。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-start-rank` 是当前节点上的第一个DP rank。节点0默认从0开始，节点1从1开始。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-address` 必须指向主DP节点。节点0上使用节点0的 `local_ip`，其他节点上使用 `node0_ip`。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-rpc-port` 是DP RPC端口。所有节点使用相同值，并确保端口可用。\n"
"- `--api-server-count` 控制主节点上启动的API服务器进程数量。\n"
"- `--headless` 启动一个不暴露API服务器的工作节点。在非主节点上使用。\n"
"- `--tensor-parallel-size 8` 将一个TP组映射到每个A2节点的8个NPU上。\n"
"- `HCCL_IF_IP`、`GLOO_SOCKET_IFNAME`、`TP_SOCKET_IFNAME` 和 `HCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME` 将HCCL、Gloo和TP通信绑定到所选网络。\n"
"- `multistream_overlap_shared_expert` 重叠共享专家计算，以提高MoE工作负载的吞吐量。"

msgid "### 5.3 Multi-Node Deployment with Ray"
msgstr "### 5.3 基于Ray的多节点部署"

msgid ""
"For Ray-based distributed deployment, refer to [Ray Distributed "
"(Qwen/Qwen3-235B-A22B)](../features/ray.md). The same model weight, "
"communication verification, and parameter tuning principles apply to "
"Qwen3.5-397B-A17B."
msgstr ""
"对于基于Ray的分布式部署，请参考[Ray分布式部署（Qwen/Qwen3-235B-A22B）](../features/ray.md)。相同的模型权重、通信验证和参数调优原则适用于Qwen3.5-397B-A17B。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If Ray workers cannot discover each other, check Ray "
"cluster status first, then verify the same HCCL and network interface "
"settings used in MP deployment."
msgstr "常见问题提示：如果Ray工作节点无法互相发现，请先检查Ray集群状态，然后验证MP部署中使用的相同HCCL和网络接口设置。"

msgid "### 5.4 Prefill-Decode Disaggregation"
msgstr "### 5.4 预填充-解码分离"

msgid ""
"PD disaggregation separates Prefill and Decode into different service "
"groups. Prefill nodes process large prompt chunks, Decode nodes serve token "
"generation, and a proxy forwards requests between them. This mode is "
"suitable for production serving scenarios where prefill and decode resource "
"ratios need to be tuned separately."
msgstr ""
"PD分离将预填充和解码分配到不同的服务组。预填充节点处理大的提示块，解码节点负责token生成，代理在它们之间转发请求。此模式适用于需要分别调整预填充和解码资源比例的生产服务场景。"

msgid ""
"We recommend using Mooncake for deployment. Refer to "
"[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md) for the "
"general PD disaggregation workflow."
msgstr ""
"我们推荐使用Mooncake进行部署。有关通用PD分离工作流程，请参考[Mooncake](../features/pd_disaggregation_mooncake_multi_node.md)。"

msgid ""
"Take Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16) as an example. We recommend deploying 1P1D with"
" 3 nodes for `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp`:"
msgstr ""
"以Atlas 800 A3（64G x 16）为例。我们推荐使用3个节点部署1P1D用于 `Qwen3.5-397B-A17B-w8a8-mtp`："

msgid ""
"- 1 Prefill node: 1 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16).\n"
"- 2 Decode nodes: 2 Atlas 800 A3 (64G x 16)."
msgstr ""
"- 1个预填充节点：1个Atlas 800 A3（64G x 16）。\n"
"- 2个解码节点：2个Atlas 800 A3（64G x 16）。"

msgid ""
"Deploy `run_p.sh`, `run_d0.sh`, and `run_d1.sh` on the corresponding nodes, "
"and deploy a proxy script on the prefill master node to forward requests."
msgstr "在相应节点上部署 `run_p.sh`、`run_d0.sh` 和 `run_d1.sh`，并在预填充主节点上部署代理脚本以转发请求。"

msgid "#### 5.4.1 Prefill Node"
msgstr "#### 5.4.1 预填充节点"

msgid "Create `run_p.sh` on the prefill node."
msgstr "在预填充节点上创建 `run_p.sh`。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If the prefill service is not ready for a long time, "
"check whether the model path is shared, `ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES` contains"
" all 16 NPUs, and the Mooncake `kv_port` is available."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果预填充服务长时间未就绪，请检查模型路径是否共享、`ASCEND_RT_VISIBLE_DEVICES` 是否包含全部16个NPU，以及"
" Mooncake `kv_port` 是否可用。"

msgid "#### 5.4.2 Decode Node 0"
msgstr "#### 5.4.2 解码节点0"

msgid "Create `run_d0.sh` on the first decode node."
msgstr "在第一个解码节点上创建 `run_d0.sh`。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If decode node 0 fails to initialize, check that "
"`MASTER_IP_ADDRESS` points to decode node 0 itself, `--data-parallel-start-"
"rank` is 0, and `kv_connector_extra_config.decode.dp_size` matches the "
"global decode DP size."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果解码节点0初始化失败，请检查 `MASTER_IP_ADDRESS` 指向解码节点0自身、`--data-parallel-"
"start-rank` 为0，以及 `kv_connector_extra_config.decode.dp_size` 与全局解码DP大小匹配。"

msgid "#### 5.4.3 Decode Node 1"
msgstr "#### 5.4.3 解码节点1"

msgid "Create `run_d1.sh` on the second decode node."
msgstr "在第二个解码节点上创建 `run_d1.sh`。"

msgid ""
"Common Issues Tip: If decode node 1 cannot join decode node 0, check that "
"`--headless` is set, `--data-parallel-start-rank` is 8, and `--data-"
"parallel-address` points to decode node 0."
msgstr ""
"常见问题提示：如果解码节点1无法加入解码节点0，请检查是否设置了 `--headless`、`--data-parallel-start-rank` "
"为8，以及 `--data-parallel-address` 指向解码节点0。"

msgid "**Key parameters for PD disaggregation:**"
msgstr "**PD分离的关键参数：**"

msgid ""
"- `--distributed-executor-backend mp` uses multiprocessing on each node for the local workers.\n"
"- Prefill uses `--data-parallel-size 8`, `--data-parallel-size-local 8`, and `--tensor-parallel-size 2`. This creates 8 local DP groups, each with TP2.\n"
"- Decode uses `--data-parallel-size 16`, `--data-parallel-size-local 8`, and `--tensor-parallel-size 2`. Decode node 0 starts from DP rank 0 and decode node 1 starts from DP rank 8.\n"
"- `--data-parallel-address` and `--data-parallel-rpc-port` define the DP control plane. For decode nodes, the address must point to decode node 0.\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` is larger on the prefill node and smaller on decode nodes because prefill is prompt-token intensive while decode is latency sensitive.\n"
"- `recompute_scheduler_enable` sends requests back to the prefill side to recompute KV cache when decode KV cache is insufficient. Enable it only on decode nodes in PD mode.\n"
"- `--kv-transfer-config` sets the Mooncake connector. `kv_role` is `kv_producer` on prefill and `kv_consumer` on decode.\n"
"- `kv_connector_extra_config.prefill.dp_size/tp_size` and `decode.dp_size/tp_size` must match the actual global DP and TP layout.\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` disables prefix caching. For PD disaggregation, the D-node prefix-cache known issue is tracked in [#7944](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/issues/7944).\n"
"- `VLLM_MOONCAKE_ABORT_REQUEST_TIMEOUT` is the timeout in seconds for automatically releasing the prefiller KV cache for a request.\n"
"- `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\": \"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` is recommended on decode nodes to reduce decode dispatch overhead."
msgstr ""
"- `--distributed-executor-backend mp` 在每个节点上使用多进程处理本地工作进程。\n"
"- 预填充使用 `--data-parallel-size 8`、`--data-parallel-size-local 8` 和 `--tensor-parallel-size 2`。这会创建8个本地DP组，每个组为TP2。\n"
"- 解码使用 `--data-parallel-size 16`、`--data-parallel-size-local 8` 和 `--tensor-parallel-size 2`。解码节点0从DP rank 0开始，解码节点1从DP rank 8开始。\n"
"- `--data-parallel-address` 和 `--data-parallel-rpc-port` 定义DP控制平面。对于解码节点，地址必须指向解码节点0。\n"
"- `--max-num-batched-tokens` 在预填充节点上较大，在解码节点上较小，因为预填充是提示词令牌密集型，而解码对延迟敏感。\n"
"- `recompute_scheduler_enable` 在解码KV缓存不足时将请求发送回预填充端重新计算KV缓存。仅在PD模式下在解码节点上启用。\n"
"- `--kv-transfer-config` 设置Mooncake连接器。`kv_role` 在预填充端为 `kv_producer`，在解码端为 `kv_consumer`。\n"
"- `kv_connector_extra_config.prefill.dp_size/tp_size` 和 `decode.dp_size/tp_size` 必须与实际全局DP和TP布局匹配。\n"
"- `--no-enable-prefix-caching` 禁用前缀缓存。对于PD分离，D节点前缀缓存的已知问题跟踪于 [#7944](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/issues/7944)。\n"
"- `VLLM_MOONCAKE_ABORT_REQUEST_TIMEOUT` 是自动释放请求预填充器KV缓存的超时时间（秒）。\n"
"- 建议在解码节点上使用 `--compilation-config '{\"cudagraph_mode\": \"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` 以减少解码调度开销。"

