msgid "## 9 Performance Tuning"
msgstr "## 9 性能调优"

msgid "### 9.1 Recommended Configurations"
msgstr "### 9.1 推荐配置"

msgid ""
"The following configurations are validated in specific test environments and"
" are for reference only. The optimal configuration depends on hardware type,"
" maximum input/output length, request concurrency, prefix cache hit rate, "
"quantization, and prefill/decode ratio. Tune the parameters in Section 9.2 "
"based on your actual workload."
msgstr ""
"以下配置在特定测试环境中经过验证，仅供参考。最佳配置取决于硬件类型、最大输入/输出长度、请求并发数、前缀缓存命中率、量化方式以及预填充/解码比例。请根据实际工作负载调整第9.2节中的参数。"

msgid "### 9.2 Tuning Guidelines"
msgstr "### 9.2 调优指南"

msgid ""
"Refer to [public performance tuning "
"documentation](../../developer_guide/performance_and_debug/optimization_and_tuning.md)"
" for general tuning methods, and refer to [feature "
"matrix](../../user_guide/support_matrix/feature_matrix.md) for feature "
"descriptions."
msgstr ""
"通用调优方法请参考[公开性能调优文档](../../developer_guide/performance_and_debug/optimization_and_tuning.md)，功能描述请参考[特性矩阵](../../user_guide/support_matrix/feature_matrix.md)。"

msgid "Recommended tuning order:"
msgstr "推荐调优顺序："

msgid ""
"1. Set the deployment topology first. Use single-node deployment for validation, MP deployment for simple multi-node serving, and PD disaggregation when prefill and decode need different resource ratios.\n"
"2. Choose the maximum context length with `--max-model-len`. Long context increases KV cache usage, so reduce `--max-num-seqs` or `--gpu-memory-utilization` if OOM occurs.\n"
"3. Tune `--max-num-batched-tokens`. Larger values usually improve prefill throughput but increase activation memory. Decode-heavy workloads usually need smaller values.\n"
"4. Tune `--max-num-seqs` according to service concurrency. Requests above this value wait in the queue and the waiting time is counted in TTFT and TPOT.\n"
"5. Tune `--gpu-memory-utilization`. Increase it to provide more KV cache, but leave headroom for runtime memory fluctuation and expert imbalance.\n"
"6. Tune `--speculative-config`. MTP can improve decode throughput, but the best `num_speculative_tokens` depends on acceptance rate and workload.\n"
"7. Tune ACLGraph capture. `FULL_DECODE_ONLY` is recommended for decode. If you set `cudagraph_capture_sizes` manually, include common decode batch sizes. With FlashComm1, use capture sizes that are multiples of TP size."
msgstr ""
"1. 首先设置部署拓扑。使用单节点部署进行验证，MP部署用于简单的多节点服务，当prefill和decode需要不同资源比例时使用PD分离。\n"
"2. 通过`--max-model-len`选择最大上下文长度。长上下文会增加KV缓存使用量，若发生OOM，请减少`--max-num-seqs`或`--gpu-memory-utilization`。\n"
"3. 调整`--max-num-batched-tokens`。较大的值通常能提升prefill吞吐，但会增加激活内存。decode密集型负载通常需要较小的值。\n"
"4. 根据服务并发度调整`--max-num-seqs`。超过此值的请求将在队列中等待，等待时间计入TTFT和TPOT。\n"
"5. 调整`--gpu-memory-utilization`。增大该值可提供更多KV缓存，但需为运行时内存波动和专家不平衡预留空间。\n"
"6. 调整`--speculative-config`。MTP可以提升decode吞吐，但最佳`num_speculative_tokens`取决于接受率和工作负载。\n"
"7. 调整ACLGraph捕获。decode推荐使用`FULL_DECODE_ONLY`。如果手动设置`cudagraph_capture_sizes`，请包含常见的decode批处理大小。使用FlashComm1时，请使用TP大小的倍数作为捕获大小。"

msgid "### 9.3 Model-Specific Optimizations"
msgstr "### 9.3 模型特定优化"

msgid "## 10 FAQ"
msgstr "## 10 常见问题"

msgid ""
"For common environment, installation, and general parameter issues, refer to"
" [FAQs](../../faqs.md). This section only covers model-specific issues for "
"Qwen3.5-397B-A17B."
msgstr "常见环境、安装及通用参数问题请参考[常见问题](../../faqs.md)。本节仅涵盖Qwen3.5-397B-A17B的模型特定问题。"

msgid ""
"### Q1: Why does the service report OOM during startup or soon after "
"accepting requests?"
msgstr "### Q1: 为什么服务在启动时或刚接受请求后报告OOM？"

msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** The service fails during profile run, or it starts "
"successfully but reports OOM when real traffic arrives."
msgstr "**现象：** 服务在profile运行期间失败，或者成功启动但在真实流量到达时报告OOM。"

msgid ""
"**Cause:** Qwen3.5-397B-A17B has high weight and KV cache memory "
"requirements. Large `--max-model-len`, large `--max-num-seqs`, large `--max-"
"num-batched-tokens`, or high `--gpu-memory-utilization` can leave "
"insufficient HBM headroom. Runtime expert load imbalance can also make real "
"inference use more memory than the profile run."
msgstr ""
"**原因：** Qwen3.5-397B-A17B 对权重和 KV 缓存的内存需求较高。较大的 `--max-model-len`、`--max-"
"num-seqs`、`--max-num-batched-tokens` 或较高的 `--gpu-memory-utilization` 可能导致 "
"HBM 余量不足。运行时专家负载不均衡也可能导致实际推理使用的内存超过性能分析运行时的内存。"

msgid ""
"**Solution:** Use the W8A8 model with `--quantization ascend` when possible,"
" lower `--max-model-len`, lower `--max-num-seqs`, lower `--max-num-batched-"
"tokens`, or reduce `--gpu-memory-utilization`. Keep "
"`PYTORCH_NPU_ALLOC_CONF=expandable_segments:True`. For BF16 or larger "
"context, use the required number of A2/A3 nodes."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 尽可能使用带有 `--quantization ascend` 的 W8A8 模型，降低 `--max-model-"
"len`、`--max-num-seqs`、`--max-num-batched-tokens` 或 `--gpu-memory-"
"utilization`。保持 `PYTORCH_NPU_ALLOC_CONF=expandable_segments:True`。对于 BF16 "
"或更大的上下文，请使用所需数量的 A2/A3 节点。"

msgid "### Q2: Why does multi-node MP deployment hang during initialization?"
msgstr "### Q2：为什么多节点 MP 部署在初始化期间会挂起？"

msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** One node waits for other ranks, HCCL initialization times "
"out, or the headless node exits."
msgstr "**现象：** 一个节点等待其他 rank，HCCL 初始化超时，或 headless 节点退出。"

msgid ""
"**Cause:** Network interface names, IP addresses, DP ranks, or RPC ports are"
" inconsistent across nodes."
msgstr "**原因：** 各节点间的网络接口名称、IP 地址、DP rank 或 RPC 端口不一致。"

msgid ""
"**Solution:** Verify multi-node communication first. Ensure `HCCL_IF_IP`, "
"`GLOO_SOCKET_IFNAME`, `TP_SOCKET_IFNAME`, and `HCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME` match the"
" selected NIC. Ensure all nodes use the same `--data-parallel-rpc-port`, "
"non-master nodes use `--headless`, and `--data-parallel-start-rank` does not"
" overlap."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 首先验证多节点通信。确保 `HCCL_IF_IP`、`GLOO_SOCKET_IFNAME`、`TP_SOCKET_IFNAME` "
"和 `HCCL_SOCKET_IFNAME` 与所选网卡匹配。确保所有节点使用相同的 `--data-parallel-rpc-port`，非主节点使用"
" `--headless`，并且 `--data-parallel-start-rank` 不重叠。"

msgid ""
"### Q3: Why is prefix caching disabled in the PD disaggregation examples?"
msgstr "### Q3：为什么在 PD 分离示例中禁用了前缀缓存？"

msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** PD disaggregation may show abnormal behavior when prefix "
"caching is enabled on decode nodes."
msgstr "**现象：** 在解码节点上启用前缀缓存时，PD 分离可能表现出异常行为。"

msgid ""
"**Cause:** The D-node prefix-cache issue is a known limitation tracked in "
"[#7944](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-ascend/issues/7944)."
msgstr ""
"**原因：** D 节点前缀缓存问题是一个已知限制，已在 [#7944](https://github.com/vllm-project/vllm-"
"ascend/issues/7944) 中跟踪。"

msgid ""
"**Solution:** Use `--no-enable-prefix-caching` for PD disaggregation until "
"the limitation is resolved. For non-PD single-node serving, enable prefix "
"caching only when the workload has repeated prefixes and the cache hit rate "
"is meaningful."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 在此限制解决之前，对 PD 分离使用 `--no-enable-prefix-caching`。对于非 PD "
"的单节点服务，仅当工作负载包含重复前缀且缓存命中率有意义时才启用前缀缓存。"

msgid ""
"### Q4: Why does performance regress after enabling FlashComm1 or Fused MC2?"
msgstr "### Q4：为什么启用 FlashComm1 或 Fused MC2 后性能会下降？"

msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** Throughput decreases, latency increases, or MoE load becomes"
" unstable after enabling communication or MoE fusion optimizations."
msgstr "**现象：** 启用通信或 MoE 融合优化后，吞吐量下降，延迟增加，或 MoE 负载变得不稳定。"

msgid ""
"**Cause:** These optimizations are workload dependent. FlashComm1 is most "
"useful in high-concurrency TP scenarios. Fused MC2 may not be suitable for "
"some multi-DP large-token cases where padded tokens overload certain "
"experts."
msgstr ""
"**原因：** 这些优化依赖于工作负载。FlashComm1 在高并发 TP 场景中最有用。Fused MC2 可能不适用于某些多 DP 大 token"
" 场景，在这些场景中，填充的 token 会使某些专家过载。"

msgid ""
"**Solution:** Compare with `enable_flashcomm1` disabled and "
"`enable_fused_mc2` set to 0. If FlashComm1 is enabled and you tune "
"`cudagraph_capture_sizes`, use values that are multiples of TP size. Keep "
"the better setting for your actual concurrency and prompt length "
"distribution."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 与禁用 `enable_flashcomm1` 并将 `enable_fused_mc2` 设置为 0 的情况进行比较。如果启用了 "
"FlashComm1 并且您调整了 `cudagraph_capture_sizes`，请使用 TP "
"大小的倍数作为值。根据您的实际并发量和提示长度分布保留更优的设置。"

msgid "### Q5: How should I tune MTP speculative decoding for this model?"
msgstr "### Q5：我应该如何为此模型调整 MTP 推测解码？"

msgid ""
"**Phenomenon:** MTP improves throughput in some workloads, but may increase "
"first-token latency or provide limited benefit in others."
msgstr "**现象：** MTP 在某些工作负载中提高了吞吐量，但在其他工作负载中可能会增加首 token 延迟或提供有限的收益。"

msgid ""
"**Cause:** The benefit depends on speculative token acceptance rate, request"
" length, and decode concurrency."
msgstr "**原因：** 收益取决于推测 token 接受率、请求长度和解码并发度。"

msgid ""
"**Solution:** Start with `num_speculative_tokens` set to 3 as shown in this "
"document. If the service is latency-sensitive or the acceptance rate is low,"
" reduce the value or remove `--speculative-config` and compare TTFT, TPOT, "
"and throughput."
msgstr ""
"**解决方案：** 从本文档所示的 `num_speculative_tokens` 设置为 3 开始。如果服务对延迟敏感或接受率较低，请减小该值或移除"
" `--speculative-config`，并比较 TTFT、TPOT 和吞吐量。"

