"across layers to reduce decode overhead. | No extra configuration is "
"required. |"
msgstr "| Rope 优化 | 默认启用 | 跨层复用位置编码计算以减少解码开销。 | 无需额外配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| AddRMSNormQuant fusion | Enabled by default | Fuses normalization and "
"quantization to reduce memory access. | Applies to quantized paths. |"
msgstr "| AddRMSNormQuant 融合 | 默认启用 | 融合归一化与量化操作以减少内存访问。 | 适用于量化路径。 |"

msgid ""
"| Zero-like elimination | Enabled by default | Removes unnecessary zero-like"
" tensor operations in attention. | No extra configuration is required. |"
msgstr "| 类零消除 | 默认启用 | 移除注意力机制中不必要的类零张量操作。 | 无需额外配置。 |"

msgid ""
"| Qwen3.5 MTP speculative decoding | `--speculative-config '{\"method\": "
"\"qwen3_5_mtp\", \"num_speculative_tokens\": 3, \"enforce_eager\": true}'` |"
" Improves decode throughput when acceptance rate is good. | Reduce "
"speculative tokens if latency or stability regresses. |"
msgstr ""
"| Qwen3.5 MTP 推测解码 | `--speculative-config '{\"method\": \"qwen3_5_mtp\", "
"\"num_speculative_tokens\": 3, \"enforce_eager\": true}'` | 在接受率良好时提升解码吞吐量。 "
"| 若延迟或稳定性下降，可减少推测 token 数量。 |"

msgid ""
"| Full decode ACLGraph | `--compilation-config "
"'{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` | Reduces operator dispatch "
"overhead and stabilizes decode performance. | Recommended for decode-heavy "
"serving. |"
msgstr ""
"| 全解码 ACLGraph | `--compilation-config "
"'{\"cudagraph_mode\":\"FULL_DECODE_ONLY\"}'` | 降低算子调度开销，稳定解码性能。 | "
"推荐用于解码密集型服务场景。 |"

msgid ""
"| FlashComm1 | `--additional-config '{\"enable_flashcomm1\": true}'` | "
"Reduces communication overhead in large TP and high-concurrency scenarios. |"
" May not help low-concurrency workloads. |"
msgstr ""
"| FlashComm1 | `--additional-config '{\"enable_flashcomm1\": true}'` | 降低大 "
"TP 和高并发场景下的通信开销。 | 对低并发工作负载可能无帮助。 |"

msgid ""
"| Fused MC2 | `--additional-config '{\"enable_fused_mc2\": 1}'` | Enables "
"MoE fused operators to improve MoE prefill/decode efficiency. | If accuracy "
"or performance regresses in multi-DP large-token scenarios, disable it and "
"compare. |"
msgstr ""
"| 融合 MC2 | `--additional-config '{\"enable_fused_mc2\": 1}'` | 启用 MoE "
"融合算子以提升 MoE 预填充/解码效率。 | 若在多 DP 大 token 场景下精度或性能下降，请禁用它并对比效果。 |"

msgid ""
"| Shared expert overlap | `--additional-config "
"'{\"multistream_overlap_shared_expert\": true}'` | Overlaps shared expert "
"computation in MoE workloads. | Recommended for MP throughput scenarios. |"
msgstr ""
"| 共享专家重叠 | `--additional-config '{\"multistream_overlap_shared_expert\": "
"true}'` | 在 MoE 工作负载中重叠共享专家计算。 | 推荐用于 MP 吞吐量场景。 |"

msgid ""
"| Recompute scheduler | `--additional-config "
"'{\"recompute_scheduler_enable\": true}'` | Recomputes KV through prefill "
"when decode KV cache is insufficient in PD mode. | Only valid on decode "
"nodes where `kv_role` is `kv_consumer`. |"
msgstr ""
"| 重计算调度器 | `--additional-config '{\"recompute_scheduler_enable\": true}'` | "
"在 PD 模式下解码 KV 缓存不足时，通过预填充重新计算 KV。 | 仅对 `kv_role` 为 `kv_consumer` 的解码节点有效。 |"

msgid ""
"| CPU binding | `--additional-config '{\"enable_cpu_binding\": true}'` | "
"Improves CPU affinity and reduces scheduling jitter on ARM servers. | "
"Enabled by default in many configurations, but explicitly setting it keeps "
"the recipe clear. |"
msgstr ""
"| CPU 绑定 | `--additional-config '{\"enable_cpu_binding\": true}'` | 提升 ARM "
"服务器上的 CPU 亲和性，减少调度抖动。 | 许多配置中默认启用，但显式设置可使配置方案更清晰。 |"
